headline: GTA Online
subtitle: On the Podium this Week: The Överflöd Entity XXR
content:
If you find yourself in the lobby of The Diamond Casino & Resort for whatever reason — maybe you were perusing the Casino Store or enjoying a free shot of Macbeth at the bar — make sure to spin the Lucky Wheel. You’re guaranteed to walk away with a prize: it could be GTA$, RP, clothing or mystery prizes.

This week’s top prize on the podium is the Överflöd Entity XXR, a Swedish-built hypercar that pairs state-of-the-art technology, Scandinavian style, and brute strength.
